title: NEWLY LISTED LUXE 2BD 1BA
posting_body: ['Description', 'Welcome to this beautiful modern designed apartment!', 'The apartment has its own balcony!!', 'Great airy layout.', 'Enjoy oversized sun-filled windows in all rooms.', 'The kitchen is fully renovated with stainless appliances, and dishwasher.', 'Very Sunny Apt!', 'There is Energy efficient Split unit Central-AC/Heat in every room.', 'Built in Bluetooth speakers in the wall.', 'Building is just a year old.', 'Friendly and responsive management.', 'Lots of great building amenities, including a gym, recreation room with tv and a pool table.', 'Plus a rooftop with lounge furniture and pristine views.', 'Great price on a no fee luxury modern apartment in a state of the art building!', 'The apartment has a super high quality and luxury vibe!', '- Laundry room', '- Bike room', '- State of the art GYM', '- Gorgeous roof with pristine views', '- Entertainment Center', '- Parking available for extra charge', 'Enjoy a walk to the park nearby!', 'Abundance of cafe’s and restaurants nearby!', 'Close Trains making commuting a breeze!']
